From the problem data, the relevant lines are:

- Depreciation20240101001 | Depreciation | 2024-01-01 | 2024-01-01 | 45748.2 | 45748.2 | ...
- Depreciation20240201002 | Depreciation | 2024-02-01 | 2024-02-01 | 54491.689999999995 | 54491.689999999995 | ...

The latest date is 2024-02-01, and the depreciation amount is 54491.69 (rounded).

Therefore, the final depreciation item in the cash flow statement is 54491.69.
